rys-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-on-birthday/">IRyS (Iris) 生日当天订阅人数突破 100 万</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“IRyS (Iris) 在她生日那天订阅人数突破 100 万” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/irys-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-on-birthday/embed/#?secret=S88FxbENob#?secret=lW7exYJsFP" data-secret="lW7exYJsFP" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="kp5pK428yy"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-reached-the-largest-youtube-subscribers-3-09-million-in-history-of-vtuber-of-japan-surpassed-kizuna-ai/">Hosho Marine 创下日本 VTuber 历史上订阅人数最多的 309 万人，超越 Kizuna AI 的纪录</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Hosho Marine 实现了日本 VTuber 历史上最多的订阅者数量，达到 309 万人，超过了 Kizuna AI 的记录” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/houshou-marine-reached-the-largest-youtube-subscribers-3-09-million-in-history-of-vtuber-of-japan-surpassed-kizuna-ai/embed/#?secret=D83oBESjfe#?secret=kp5pK428yy" data-secret="kp5pK428yy" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="evzrcW1sfz"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/himemori-luna-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-hololive-4th-gen-all-vtuber-reached/">Luna Himemori 订阅用户突破100万 Hololive第四代VTuber全部突破100万</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Luna Himemori 订阅者数量达到 100 万。所有 Hololive 第四代 VTuber 数量达到 100 万” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/himemori-luna-reached-1-million-youtube-sub