utube.com/channel/UC0TXe_LYZ4scaW2XMyi5_kw" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">AZKi 频道</a>/ <a href="https://twitter.com/AZKi_VDiVA" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">AZKi <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2692.png" alt="⚒" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></a> / <a href="https://hololive.hololivepro.com/talents/azki/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">阿兹基</a></p><cite>YouTube / Twitter / Hololive 制作</cite></blockquote><p>（ <em>P2y.jp管理代表“Mr.2”</em> /Virtual Metaverse/VTuber信息） </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Gc66W4iAS7"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/azki-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-all-hololive-0-gen-reached-1m/">AZKi 频道订阅人数突破 100 万 Hololive 0 代会员全部 5 名订阅人数突破 100 万</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“AZKi 频道订阅人数突破 100 万 Hololive 第 0 代 5 名成员全部突破 100 万” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/azki-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-all-hololive-0-gen-reached-1m/embed/#?secret=G8huZFEUBm#?secret=Gc66W4iAS7" data-secret="Gc66W4iAS7" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><p></p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/azki-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-all-hololive-0-gen-reached-1m/">AZKi 频道后订阅人数突破 100 万 Hololive 0 代成员全部 5 名</a>首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; https://p2y.jp/azki-reached-1-million-youtube-subscribers-all-hololive-0-gen-reached-1m/feed/ 0 123652
青桐高中成为 VTuber 机构/团体历史上第三个拥有 100 万订阅者的官方频道。 https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agcies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/ https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agcies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/#respondp2y_admin Sat, 27 Apr 2024 06:11:34 +0000 VTuberバーチャルTwitterYouTubeYouTuberあおぎり高校チャンネル登録者数(YouTube)バーチャルYouTuber https://p2y.jp/?p=123747 <p>截至2024年4月26日（令和6年）12点，VTuber团体青桐高中官方YouTube频道订阅人数已达100万，为VTuber机构和团体历史上第三位[…]</p> <a href="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agencies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/">青桐高中成为 VTuber 机构/团体历史上第三个拥有 100 万订阅者的官方频道</a>后，首次出现在<a href="https://p2y.jp">P2y.jp</a>上。; <p></p><p>截至2024年4月26日（令和6年）12点，VTuber团体<strong>青桐高中</strong>官方YouTube频道订阅人数已突破100万，成为历史上第三个VTuber机构/团体。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="674" data-attachment-id="123753" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/aogiri-high-school-became-the-3rd-vtuber-agencies-and-groups-in-history-to-reach-1-million-official-youtube-subscribers/aogiri_high_school_became_the_3rd_vtuber_agencies_and_groups_in_history_to_reach_1_million_official_youtube_subscribers/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/aogiri_high_school_became_the_3rd_vtuber_agencies_and_groups_in_history_to_reach_1_million_official_youtube_subscribers.png" data-orig-size="1200,674" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="あおぎり高校 VTuber事務所・グループ史上3番目の公式チャンネル登録者数100万人を達成" data-image-description="&lt;p>;あおぎり高校 VTuber事務所・グループ史上3番目の公式チャンネル登録者数100万人を達成&lt;/p>;
