</style><h2 id="outline__5" class="wp-block-heading">40万人</h2><h3 id="outline__5_1" class="wp-block-heading" id="outline__8_2">京堡</h3><figure class="wp-block-image"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="1200" height="675" data-attachment-id="74369" data-permalink="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-youtube-subscribers-information-14-october-2022/jingburger_youtube_channel_14_october_2022/" data-orig-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/jingburger_youtube_channel_14_october_2022.jpg" data-orig-size="1200,675" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="jingburger_youtube_channel_14_october_2022" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/jingburger_youtube_channel_14_october_2022.jpg" data-large-file="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/jingburger_youtube_channel_14_october_2022.jpg" src="https://p2y.jp/wp-content/uploads/2022/10/jingburger_youtube_channel_14_october_2022.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-74369"/><figcaption class="wp-element-caption"> 징버거 JINGBURGER（截至2022年10月14日）</figcaption></figure><figure class="wp-block-table is-style-stripes"><table><tbody><tr><td>人才名称</td><td>注册人数（较1个月前增减）</td></tr><tr><td>辛伯格<br>(JINGBURGER (징버거))</td><td> 401,000 人（+8000 人）</td></tr></tbody></table><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">截至 2024 年 4 月 26 日 0:00 </figcaption></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote is-layout-flow wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow"><p><a href="https://youtube.com/%EC%A7%95%EB%B2%84%EA%B1%B0" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">JINGBURGER</a> /<a href="https://twitter.com/